Package level2Assignment1

Class EMRecord

java.lang.Object
level2Assignment1.EMHRecord
level2Assignment1.EMRecord
public class EMRecord extends EMHRecord
Represents an electronic medical record (EMR) for a patient, extending the EMHRecord with patient-specific details like height and weight. This class supports basic patient information management and calculation of Body Mass Index (BMI) based on the patient's height and weight.
